summary: TK children patches for a variety of mods
descriptionHtml:
The old ETaC patches are outdated, and causes ctds. I will redo the patch once missjenabee finishes doing Falkreath.

My TK children for Inconsequential NPCs requires the updated, 1.8 version of the original mod.
My version is an improved, up to date, bug free version (the version made by nonoodles face tint, skin color and mesh bugs).

Don't forget to check out [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51886/?]the patch for the USKP, which also comes in a merged plugin version[/url]
author: thordir
